ought trapped within her mind was to kill. With all this racing through her head fueling her but not about to be let loose she would look to Callisto and with the look she possessed within those eye's her affection, her gratitude, the bond she offered and the comfort she felt could all be scene directed toward Callisto. Then the the fire within her would reach its horrid peak, Vengeance must be taken, they must pay for what they had done. She then walked past her friend and out of the hut stopping just before its entrance outside to scream as loud as she could~<br>
