<br>
&quot;I'm not loosing another person I love - even if I have to personally go down to the underworld and get her back.&quot;<br>
<br>
She sighed and began to clean the blood from Alysia's body. Unsuccessfully, of course, considering she was still covered in the blood of the centaurs who had stood in her path as she went to Aly.<br>
<br>
She pulled up a chair and sat beside Aly's lifeless body, silently praying that she'd return.. She had to.<br>
<br>
